body:
Data files for L1T **Phase2** Muon algorithms, one for L1T reco and one for L1T Trigger Primitives
   * L1T algorithm for Track + EMTFtrack / EMTFstub
   * RPC TriggerPrimitives  (needed for https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/26967)
title: Data files for Phase2 L1T algorithm EMTF and Phase2 RPC TriggerPrimitives
